                  , <rs id="t17751018-58-viclabel268" type="occupation">spinster</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17751018-58-victim496 t17751018-58-viclabel268"></join>. A green silk brocaded sacque and coat, value four pounds; one crimson sacque and coat, trimmed with blond lace, value ten pounds; a gold and silver tissue sacque and coat, value fifteen pounds; a black laced silk cloak, value twenty shillings; six yards and a half of crimson silk, value three pounds; a silver dressing box, value four pounds; two pair of gauze ruffles, value twenty shillings; a pair of lace ruffles, value three pounds; and two black laced handkerchiefs, value five shillings, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17751018-58-victim498" type="victimName">
                           Frances
                            Mostyn
